{
  "stem": "5371.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was mixed in with them, so I had a chance to run into my block, to my barrack, empty it out, and I just walk out and that's it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, anyway I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From then on, in fact I had a case once while on the job.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was already in 1944 where the Russians-- where the Russians were already pushing the Germans back, where they lost the Stalingrad war, you know, battle.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somehow these SS, we had the head of the SS, [INAUDIBLE] four SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had one SS head, which was an oberscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a Dutch German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know if they were turning a new leaf or not, but he became all of a sudden very friendly, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said to me already, you know, if I can get gold, or diamonds, or gold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I wouldn't take a chance with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But one evening, they got all drunk, the SS guards and all the Polacks, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were all drunk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, you know, we have to go back to camp and you cannot go back to camp drunk, because we-- they put us [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They are like [INAUDIBLE] kommando.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was like one group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If they-- if you, you know, they, you know, committed some kind of infraction or-- or crime, they put you in that kommando and you know you were finished.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was carrying four rifles and four dogs and on leashes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were going with back roads to camp till they sobered out a little bit and we went into camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this-- there was-- this-- this incident happened only once.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
